  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/16026161755f6d93ea6feff8fa35489b.poster.avif?t=1711370452\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/16026161755f6d93ea6feff8fa35489b.webm?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/16026161755f6d93ea6feff8fa35489b.mp4?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Voxel Battle Simulator is a voxel-based tactical game.<br>Deploy your units on the battlefield and watch as the struggle unfolds in this simple and humorous, voxel-based tactical game. Featuring 90 levels of a single player campaign spread across 6 different world environments. Pit units against each other in the sandbox mode and see which army comes out on top once everything turns to rubble.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/42640181ef3a21d5935115d464bf8bf1.avif?t=1711370452\" width=620 height=79 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/3877fe8ae64bf772b5a73204878214b9.poster.avif?t=1711370452\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/3877fe8ae64bf772b5a73204878214b9.webm?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/3877fe8ae64bf772b5a73204878214b9.mp4?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Strategize</strong> the flow of battle<br></li><li><strong>Deploy</strong> the units<br></li><li><strong>Observe</strong> the battle unfold<br></li><li><strong>Destroy</strong> environment<br></li><li><strong>Compete</strong> with your friends in a local multiplayer</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/508171c49e2198f589c4cac5592f6a17.avif?t=1711370452\" width=620 height=79 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/ea3be08bf836f980bce6bd040084c170.poster.avif?t=1711370452\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/ea3be08bf836f980bce6bd040084c170.webm?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/ea3be08bf836f980bce6bd040084c170.mp4?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you overcome all the challenges throughout different environments, adapt upon seeing different enemy strategies and fulfill the expectations of the general. Unlock new units and upgrade existing ones.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/9fcdeef1d41d8734f2a0cc5faabe6b93.avif?t=1711370452\" width=620 height=79 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/85cb0bb74246a952c590bbdcbb82d9c1.poster.avif?t=1711370452\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/85cb0bb74246a952c590bbdcbb82d9c1.webm?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501530/extras/85cb0bb74246a952c590bbdcbb82d9c1.mp4?t=1711370452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fully customize and plan your own battles. Fight against your friends in a local PvP mode. Play on 90 maps with a bunch of silly units.",
